name: A broken world through shortsighted #002
description: Got an idea from this period that I work full time and wear glasses all the time + and wear masks that make my ears hurt. break time or leave work I'll take off my glasses to make it less painful. I am short sighted make time off work There will be a lot of cars on the road. the driver went home causing the light to be flickering, eye pain, and the image that looks at it will be blurry Like the world is shaking I saw that it was interesting so I took this idea to photograph. Thank you google translate
